Manchester United midfielder Ander Herrera and Tottenham striker Fernando Llorente are transfer targets for Athletic Bilbao, according to the club&rsquo;s new director of football Rafa Alkorta. <br />
<br />
In an interview with Spanish radio network Cadena SER, Alkorta said: &quot;We are interested in Javi Martinez, Ibai Gomez, <span style="color: red;"><strong>Ander Herrera</strong></span>, Fernando Llorente... all of them interest us.&quot;

